Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
model.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object

      public Appointment(int apptID, String apptTitle, String description, String location, String apptType, LocalDateTime startDateTime, LocalDateTime endDateTime, LocalDateTime createDate, String createdBy, LocalDateTime lastUpdate, String lastUpdatedBy, int customerID, int userID, int contactID)
      This is the Appointment constructor. The Appointment constructor is used to initialize Appointment objects.
      Parameters:
      apptID - The id of the appointment.
      apptTitle - The title of the appointment.
      description - The description of the appointment.
      location - The location of the appointment.
      apptType - The type of the appointment.
      startDateTime - The start date/time of the appointment.
      endDateTime - The end date/time of the appointment.
      createDate - The date the appointment was created.
      createdBy - The user who created the appointment.
      lastUpdate - The date/time that the appointment was last updated.
      lastUpdatedBy - The user who last updated this appointment
      customerID - The customer's ID that the appointment is with.
      contactID - The contact ID for the appointment.
      userID - The user ID who created the appointment.
